addOrMerge

public void addOrMerge(E child)
If the child expression is a Parameter that has the same name as an existing child, then it would be merged with that. If Comparison, then the range of the original would be set (and possibly tightened). If Parameter, then there actually is a contradiction, and would be ignored.

child -
